org.mt4j.input.inputSources
Class TuioInputSource

java.lang.Object
  org.mt4j.input.inputSources.AbstractInputSource
      org.mt4j.input.inputSources.TuioInputSource
All Implemented Interfaces:
TUIO.TuioListener
public class TuioInputSource
extends AbstractInputSource
implements TUIO.TuioListener

This class implements the TuioListener interface and generates TouchEvents with associated Cursors. It then passes them on to the registered Listeners that have to implement the IinputSourceListener interface.

Author:
Christopher Ruff
